<p>The content halves pattern contains two, equal-width content columns. There is the option of a heading above the columns and a full-width background colour.</p>

<h3>Rules for content halves</h3>

<ul>
	<li>The <a href="#announcements">announcements</a> option may have content in only one column.</li>
    <li>All other options must have content in both columns.</li>
	<li>Images must not be used in either column.</li>
	<li>A video may be used in the right-hand column.</li>
	<li>Accordions may be used in either column.</li>
    <li>The background colour must be either white or grey.</li>
</ul>

